# imported from FreeBSD on july 27 1998
#
# New ports collection makefile for:	kterm
# Version required:	6.2
# Date created:		18 November 1994
# Whom:			asami
#
# $Id: Makefile,v 1.16 1997/12/25 22:29:38 asami Exp $
@

